name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.namenode.max.slowpeer.collect.nodes
description:
How many slow nodes we will collect for filtering out
    when choosing targets for blocks.

    It is ignored if dfs.namenode.block-placement-policy.exclude-slow-nodes.enabled is false.

name: hadoop.http.idle_timeout.ms
description: NN/JN/DN Server connection timeout in milliseconds.

name: fs.ftp.host.port
description: FTP filesystem connects to fs.ftp.host on this port

name: dfs.qjournal.finalize-segment.timeout.ms
description:
Quorum timeout in milliseconds during finalizing for a specific
    segment.

name: dfs.datanode.max.disks.to.report
description:
Number of disks to include in JSON report per operation. We will return
    disks with the highest latency.

name: dfs.client.block.write.locateFollowingBlock.retries
description: Number of retries to use when finding the next block during HDFS writes.
